---
title: Fusilli Aglio e Olio with Zucchini and Smoked Mozzarella
description: Aglio e olio is a staple Italian pasta dish, using simple ingredients like garlic and chili flakes to create big flavours! Lightly toasting garlic in olive oil is what gives this dish its signature flavour – if you love garlic, you'll love this dish!
